<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AIOT 專題實作 - 智慧居家控制系統</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;700&family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fbff;
            color: #2d3748;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .hero-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
        }

        .section-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid #edf2f7;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .section-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.1);
        }

        .img-container {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .img-container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .step-number {
            background: #1e3a8a;
            color: white;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 16px;
        }

        .feature-tag {
            background: #eff6ff;
            color: #1e40af;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 99px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 1px solid #dbeafe;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- 頂部導航 -->
    <nav class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-50 border-b shadow-sm">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="portfolio.html" class="text-blue-800 font-bold flex items-center hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">
                <i class="fas fa-chevron-left mr-2"></i> 返回主頁
            </a>
            <h1 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">AIOT 專題實作報告</h1>
            <div class="w-10"></div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 英雄區塊 -->
    <header class="hero-gradient text-white py-24 px-6 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="inline-block bg-white/20 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold mb-6 tracking-widest uppercase">高二專題實作</div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight">智慧居家：基於物聯網的<br>多功能監控與自動化系統</h2>
            <p class="text-blue-50 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed opacity-90">
                結合 ESP32、RFID 與 Blynk 雲端平台，打造具備安全驗證與即時監控能力的智慧門禁系統。
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-20 px-6">
        
        <!-- 摘要與動機 -->
        <section class="mb-24">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-start">
                <div class="md:col-span-2">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
                        <div class="step-number">壹</div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">研究動機與摘要</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        觀察到現代家居對於安全性與便利性的需求日益增長，電子鎖已成為主流。本專題旨在開發一套整合人體紅外線偵測、門磁開關與 RFID 驗證的系統，並透過物聯網技術實現遠端監控。
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-blue-800">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt mr-3"></i> 安全性：RFID 二次驗證
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-blue-800">
                            <i class="fas fa-cloud mr-3"></i> 便利性：Blynk 雲端即時連動
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-3">
                    <div class="img-container shadow-md">
                        <img src="" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 硬體架構與概念圖 -->
        <section class="mb-24">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-10">
                <div class="step-number">貳</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">系統架構與設計流程</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="section-card p-10">
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div class="img-container">
                        <img src="" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-6 text-blue-900">核心硬體整合</h4>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-6">
                            <span class="feature-tag">ESP32 開發板</span>
                            <span class="feature-tag">RFID-RC522</span>
                            <span class="feature-tag">人體紅外線 PIR</span>
                            <span class="feature-tag">門磁開關</span>
                            <span class="feature-tag">SG90 伺服馬達</span>
                            <span class="feature-tag">蜂鳴器警報</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            系統利用 ESP32 作為運算核心，整合多種傳感器。當 PIR 偵測到人體移動時啟動系統，並透過 RFID 讀取卡片 UID，若驗證正確則由伺服馬達開啟大門。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 程式邏輯實踐 -->
        <section class="mb-24">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-10">
                <div class="step-number">參</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">程式邏輯與開發實踐</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="md:col-span-2">
                    <!-- 改為照片展示欄位 -->
                    <div class="img-container shadow-md">
                        <img src="" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-center border border-blue-100">
                    <h4 class="font-bold mb-4 text-blue-800">演算法控制邏輯</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        在程式開發中，我實作了 RFID 的卡片比對邏輯，並結合 <code>Blynk</code> 函式庫進行 Wi-Fi 連線與手機端通知。此外，透過門磁開關的狀態判斷，確保大門關閉後自動執行鎖定指令。
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-6">
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-blue-400 font-bold tracking-tighter uppercase">Programming Framework</span>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 italic mt-1">Arduino IDE / C++ Environment</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 研究結果展示 -->
        <section class="mb-24">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-10">
                <div class="step-number">肆</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">研究結果與功能驗證</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-blue-900 border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4">裝置全景與結構</h4>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div class="img-container aspect-square">
                            <img src="" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="img-container aspect-square">
                            <img src="" alt="">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm italic">研究裝置的正視圖與側視圖，展現硬體組裝的完整度。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-blue-900 border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4">功能運作情境</h4>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="w-24 h-16 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0">
                                <img src="" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h5 class="font-bold text-sm">驗證通過：開啟大門</h5>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">正確卡片感應後，綠燈亮起且馬達轉動。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="w-24 h-16 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0">
                                <img src="" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h5 class="font-bold text-sm">驗證失敗：警報響起</h5>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">未授權卡片觸發紅燈與蜂鳴器。 </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 總結與未來展望 -->
        <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-16 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="relative z-10">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 flex items-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-yellow-400 mr-4"></i> 研究總結與反思
                </h3>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-blue-100 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            在此次研究中，我不僅成功模擬了智慧居家系統的實用性，也展示了在技術整合與問題解決方面的能力。特別是在排除 I2C 通訊衝突與優化門磁靈敏度的過程中，獲得了寶貴的實務經驗。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <h5 class="text-blue-300 font-bold text-sm uppercase">未來改善方向：</h5>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-blue-100">
                            <li><i class="fas fa-arrow-right mr-2 text-blue-400"></i> 整合更完善的遠端警報通知系統</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-arrow-right mr-2 text-blue-400"></i> 加入人臉辨識模組進行三重驗證</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-arrow-right mr-2 text-blue-400"></i> 優化門磁連動機制以提高上鎖精準度</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="bg-white border-t py-16 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4">AIOT Smart Home Project Portfolio</p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-[10px]">© 2024 CHANG PO CHUAN. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
